  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Sri Krishna Kummara\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                                                                            <a>Sri Krishna Kummara</a>\n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/87654367/TNN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TNN</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Jul 22, 2026 at 03:29 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p><a href=\"/tag/vijayawada\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vijayawada</a>: In the wake of <a href=\"/tag/andhra+pradesh\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Andhra Pradesh</a> reporting sporadic covid cases across the state, the state government stepped up the <a href=\"/tag/covid-19+preparedness\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Covid-19 preparedness</a> by directing all <a href=\"/tag/government+hospitals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">government hospitals</a> to remain on high alert.As part of the measures to handle the rising Covid-19 cases and ensure treatment for the patients at the government hospitals, the government has readied 255 dedicated beds in all 17 teaching hospitals, while secondary hospitals have also been instructed to earmark beds based on local requirements.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Teaching hospitals currently have 6.78 lakh triple-layer masks, while another 5.26 lakh masks are available in central drug warehouses. In addition, 58,790 N95 masks, 4,436 PPE kits and 2,572 sanitiser bottles have been stocked. Officials said adequate quantities of antibiotics, IV fluids and other medicines required for Covid treatment are also available.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>On Tuesday, secretary (Medical&amp;Health) <a href=\"/tag/g+veerapandian\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">G Veerapandian</a> chaired a virtual meeting with the senior officials within the medical and health department and reviewed the state’s Covid-19 preparedness and directed officials concerned to evolve phased-action plans based for tackling the rising cases in the state.To speed up emergency response, the DME recently authorised hospital superintendents to procure <a href=\"/tag/remdesivir\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Remdesivir</a> injections, testing kits, sanitisers and other essential supplies through local purchases, eliminating delays associated with central procurement.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>As part of statewide preparedness, <a href=\"/tag/apmsidc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">APMSIDC</a> has placed orders for 51,700 RNA extraction kits, 27,552 <a href=\"/tag/rt-pcr+kits\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RT-PCR kits</a>, PCR consumables, filter tips, microtubes and nitrile gloves. It has also initiated the supply of 50 Remdesivir injections to each hospital. Distribution of PCR strips and filter tips has already begun, while the remaining materials are expected to reach hospitals within the next two days.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Acting on the directions of health minister <a href=\"/tag/satya+kumar+yadav\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Satya Kumar Yadav</a>, officials have ensured the availability of testing kits, medicines, <a href=\"/tag/dedicated+covid+beds\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">dedicated Covid beds</a>, personal protective equipment (PPE) and other emergency supplies across the state. During a review meeting last week, the minister said the public need not worry but instructed the Health Department to stay vigilant and ensure prompt testing and treatment for suspected cases.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>The medical and health department authorities reiterated that the state is continuously monitoring the Covid-19 situation and advised people with symptoms to visit the nearest government hospital for testing and treatment.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Sri Krishna Kummara</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Sri Krishna Kummara</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/87654367/TNN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TNN</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jul 22, 2026 at 03:29 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jul 22, 2026 at 03:29 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">2 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"App Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-app-store.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                        </div>    -->\n                         \n                \n                                    <figure>\n                        <!-- <i></i>\n                        <span class=\"scan-text\">Scan to download App</span> -->\n                        <img src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/bar-codes/health_barcode.png?mod=3407\" alt=\"\">                        \n                        <!-- <span class=\"border-bottom\